# Marlin Processor Overview

This page lists all Marlin processors available in the Key4hep software stack,
collected from the active environment. Use the search box to filter by processor
name, package, or library. Click a package header to collapse or expand it; click
a processor name to reveal its parameters.

Total: **{{ total_algorithms }} processors** across **{{ total_packages }} packages**.

```{raw} html
<style>
{% include "_overview_common.css.jinja2" %}
#algorithm-overview .alg-props-table td:nth-child(3) {
  max-width: 20em;
}
#algorithm-overview .alg-props-table td:nth-child(3) code {
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  word-break: break-word;
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
}
</style>

<div id="algorithm-overview">
  <div class="alg-filter-bar">
    <input type="text" id="alg-search" placeholder="Filter by name, package, or library…" autocomplete="off" />
    <span id="alg-stats">Showing {{ total_algorithms }} of {{ total_algorithms }} algorithms in {{ total_packages }} packages</span>
  </div>

  {%- for package, processors in packages.items() %}
  <div class="alg-package-group" data-package="{{ package | e }}">
    <div class="alg-package-header">
      <span class="alg-package-name">{{ (package if package else "(unknown)") | e }}</span>
      <span class="alg-package-meta">
        <span class="alg-package-count">{{ processors | length }} algorithm{%- if processors | length != 1 %}s{%- endif %}</span>
        <span class="alg-package-toggle">&#9660;</span>
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="alg-cards-container">
      {%- for proc in processors %}
      <div class="alg-card" data-name="{{ proc.name | e }}" data-lib="{{ proc.lib | e }}" data-package="{{ package | e }}">
        <div class="alg-card-header">
          <span class="alg-name">{{ proc.name | e }}</span>
          <span class="alg-card-right">
            {%- if proc.lib %}
            <span class="alg-lib-badge">{{ proc.lib | e }}</span>
            {%- endif %}
            <span class="alg-card-toggle">&#9658;</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="alg-card-body">
          {%- if proc.description %}
          <p class="alg-description">{{ proc.description | e }}</p>
          {%- endif %}
          {%- if proc.properties %}
          <table class="alg-props-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Parameter</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Default</th>
                <th>Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {%- for prop_name, prop_info in proc.properties.items() %}
              <tr>
                <td><code>{{ prop_name | e }}</code></td>
                <td><code>{{ prop_info.get("type", "") | e }}</code></td>
                <td>{{ prop_info.value | render_prop_value }}</td>
                <td>{{ prop_info.description | e }}</td>
              </tr>
              {%- endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
          {%- else %}
          <em>No parameters available.</em>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>

<script>
{% include "_overview_common.js.jinja2" %}
</script>
```
